# Financial Analysis – The Coca-Cola Company

## Overview
This project involved a financial analysis of Coca-Cola using the CORE framework as part of my MBA.

## Tools Used
- Microsoft Excel

## Key Analysis
- Revenue growth and profitability trends (2020–2023)
- Financial ratios (ROCE, operating margin, liquidity, gearing)
- External factors (inflation, post-pandemic recovery)

## Key Insights
- Strong revenue growth with improving capital efficiency
- Slight decline in margins due to rising costs
- Stable financial position compared to competitors

## Outcome
Achieved a Distinction (74%) and provided an investment recommendation based on financial performance.
